                      >gaaltijekovde</a>.
                  </td>
                </tr>
                </table>
              </li>
              <li>Sirtieh dejtie zhfst-fijlide akten katalogese:
                  <ul>
                    <li>Windows: <code>&lt;User&gt;\AppData\Local\voikko\3</code><br/>
                    (≤ Windows 7: <code>C:\Documents and Settings\&lt;User&gt;\Local
                    Settings\Application Data\voikko\3</code>)</li>
                    <li>OSX: <code>~/Library/Spelling/voikko/3</code></li>
                    <li>Linux: <code>~/.voikko/3</code></li>
                  </ul>
                  dejtie fijlide maahtah jeatjah sæjjan aaj bïejedh, dan bïjre
                  maahath daesnie lohkedh <a
                  href="https://github.com/voikko/corevoikko/blob/master/libvoikko/README"
                  >daesnie</a>. Ohtsedh dam bijjietjaalegem «Search order for
                  dictionary files». Mujhtieh iktesh tjoeverh tsagkedh dejtie
                  fijlide <code>.zhfst</code>-filene
                  aktene katalogese, man nomme lea «3»
              </li>
              <li>Loggh olkese jïh dle sïjse vihth</li>
            </ol>

            <p> Jis daarpesjh jeatjah gïelh, dle daesnie gååvnesieh <a
            href="http://divvun.org/">divvun.org</a>.</p>

